title: Slimpoke on Becoming an Adult Star, Brian Pumper, Cucking Dudes & More
description:
Adam called AD and T-Rell for this fire new interview with the one and only Slim Poke! He talks about his start up in the industry, making money, taking care of his health, his favorite girls to work with and more!

00:00 Intro
0:03 - Adam prefaces the pod by addressing AD and T-Rell’s reluctance to talk to Adam about his career
0:57 - Slimpoke is a full time D-slanger. Adam is part-time
1:48 - The stigma of the industry in his community
5:07 - Slim and Adam explain how they learn new tricks from watching other actors
6:20 - Adam: “Slim’s got a fire one”
7:03 - Slim on being treated like a celebrity when he goes back to the hood
7:43 - Slim's DJ career before getting into this
9:00 - Discovering he had a big one
10:38 - Slim explains how to break into the industry
11:49 - Unexpectedly doing his first movie in 2011. Having trouble performing during his first shoot
13:32 - T-Rell doesn’t understand how Adam and Slim still enjoy all this
14:14 - Slim explains his strategies for maintaining control of his member
18:38 - Slim’s homie fought another male actor on set
19:03 - Slim explains his strategy for getting through DPs and group action with 2 guys. Adam has never done a DP
20:33 - Adam is not interested in Lena working with other guys
23:30 - Fave girls to work with: Teanna Trump, Riley Reid, Bella Danger
24:17 - Slim on his relationship with Celina Powell
28:34 - Slim on being paid by husbands to do their wives
31:08 - Brian Pumper’s weird personality
33:21 - Doing it in front of 300 people at a mansion party
43:28 - His Mom’s friends are always trying to "see" him
45:19 - Slim commends Adam for his approach to the industry
48:27 - How OnlyFans has changed the game
49:57 - Responding to Sneako saying the industry is bad for young men and society
52:01 - T-Rell reveals that he was on set for the recording of Tyga’s adult shoot
55:42 - Slim says the going rate is $400-$500 per movie for a new comer
58:42 - Charging $5K for paid consultations with guys who are looking to get in the game
1:02:45 - Adam, AD, T-Rell and Slim all do T-Rell’s “row the boat” motion in unison
